20
00:02:47,708 --> 00:02:48,875
Yeah, I know.

21
00:02:48,958 --> 00:02:50,041
What if you caught a cold?

22
00:02:50,125 --> 00:02:51,666
That would be terrible.

23
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:53,833
Keep in mind I couldn't
care less if a garbage girl

24
00:02:53,916 --> 00:02:55,500
were to catch a cold.

25
00:02:55,583 --> 00:02:58,041
I just know there's a chance
it could spread to me,

26
00:02:58,125 --> 00:02:59,916
and I don't have
the time to get sick.

27
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,583
Gimme that.

28
00:03:01,666 --> 00:03:03,416
I'll give it back
to Kanade for you.

29
00:03:13,708 --> 00:03:15,000
[TAGA]
What's up with him?

30
00:03:15,083 --> 00:03:16,333
Why come home
just to turn around

31
00:03:16,416 --> 00:03:18,125
and go right back to school?

32
00:03:18,208 --> 00:03:19,625
[KANADE]
Sorry 'bout that, Sadako...

33
00:03:19,708 --> 00:03:21,708
Jeez, you got soaked.

34
00:03:21,791 --> 00:03:23,708
I was gonna bring
you an umbrella,

35
00:03:23,791 --> 00:03:26,208
but on the way, I sorta had
to give it to someone else.

36
00:03:27,625 --> 00:03:28,791
Who's there?!

37
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,541
[KANADE]
Taga!

38
00:03:31,625 --> 00:03:32,750
Who's that?

39
00:03:32,833 --> 00:03:35,958
Sadako, was it? Well, well...

40
00:03:36,041 --> 00:03:38,416
You could at least introduce us.

41
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:41,833
You said you didn't hide
anything from me, didn't you?

42
00:03:41,916 --> 00:03:43,958
Can we please
keep this between us?

43
00:03:44,041 --> 00:03:47,666
I'm begging you.
Don't tell Kaho!

44
00:03:47,750 --> 00:03:48,750
Why not?

45
00:03:48,833 --> 00:03:50,291
Because I don't
think they're ready

46
00:03:50,375 --> 00:03:52,250
to meet each other just yet.

47
00:03:52,333 --> 00:03:53,583
But besides that,

48
00:03:53,666 --> 00:03:57,250
I want to be the one
to explain this to Kaho.

49
00:03:57,333 --> 00:03:58,500
[TAGA]
Understood.

50
00:03:58,583 --> 00:04:00,875
Consider this our little secret.

51
00:04:00,958 --> 00:04:02,916
Do you wanna
pinky swear on it?

52
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,458
It's not just our secret.

53
00:04:04,541 --> 00:04:06,000
The guys know, too.

54
00:04:06,083 --> 00:04:08,041
This is a big deal.

55
00:04:08,125 --> 00:04:11,000
A promise among men...
on our honor.

56
00:04:13,791 --> 00:04:16,541
It appears that you've
gone and grown up, Kanade.

57
00:04:16,625 --> 00:04:17,916
Good for you.

58
00:04:25,958 --> 00:04:26,916
Silly boy.

59
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,833
He sure was in a hurry, huh?

60
00:04:32,416 --> 00:04:33,958
[KAHO]
A paper airplane?

61
00:04:39,916 --> 00:04:42,791
[KAHO] It's an announcement
for Kanade's sports festival.

62
00:04:42,875 --> 00:04:45,458
This is probably a
pretty important paper.

63
00:04:47,708 --> 00:04:50,791
[KAHO]
Is that... Kanade's diary?

64
00:04:50,875 --> 00:04:52,958
