even put in there...

65
00:04:53,041 --> 00:04:55,375
Does he actually write
down his feelings?

66
00:04:57,541 --> 00:04:59,166
[KAHO] It doesn't matter
what he writes in there.

67
00:04:59,250 --> 00:05:02,291
Reading his diary
is totally wrong.

68
00:05:02,375 --> 00:05:03,708
[TAGA]
I just realized...

69
00:05:03,791 --> 00:05:06,583
I bet Kanade doesn't even
think of you as a woman.

70
00:05:07,875 --> 00:05:11,000
[KAHO]
But... what if he...

71
00:05:11,083 --> 00:05:13,583
You shouldn't be
doing this, Kaho!

72
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:18,583
[KAHO] "I want to be
with her every day..."

73
00:05:18,666 --> 00:05:20,791
[KANADE] "...and I want
us to be together forever."

74
00:05:20,875 --> 00:05:22,208
"Every day when I get home,

75
00:05:22,291 --> 00:05:24,916
I'm worried someone
else will take her away.

76
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,416
But I know...

77
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:29,166
