Kaho about Sadako very soon...

78
00:05:29,250 --> 00:05:31,583
It's my new critical mission."

79
00:05:31,666 --> 00:05:34,250
[KAHO]
What? He what?

80
00:05:34,333 --> 00:05:37,250
Who is this... this Sadako?

81
00:05:37,333 --> 00:05:38,833
[TAGA]
Unbelievable.

82
00:05:38,916 --> 00:05:42,541
Reading your boyfriend's
diary... That's low.

83
00:05:42,625 --> 00:05:44,166
It really is true, then.

84
00:05:46,083 --> 00:05:47,958
You are basic trash.

85
00:05:59,458 --> 00:06:01,916
[sighing]

86
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,791
[CHIAKI] If you keep
on sighing like that,

87
00:06:03,875 --> 00:06:05,833
