happiness away.

88
00:06:05,916 --> 00:06:07,583
[KAHO]
Too late, Chiaki.

89
00:06:07,666 --> 00:06:11,541
I think happiness has run away
with its tail between its legs.

90
00:06:11,625 --> 00:06:14,333
[CHIAKI] Don't tell me...
It's about Kanade?

91
00:06:14,416 --> 00:06:16,375
[KAHO] Maybe elementary
school kids ought to date

92
00:06:16,458 --> 00:06:19,583
other elementary
school kids after all.

93
00:06:19,666 --> 00:06:21,916
[CHIAKI] What makes you say
that at this stage of the game?

94
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:24,708
I thought the plan was to wait
and see how he matures.

95
00:06:24,791 --> 00:06:27,416
Yeah, it was,
but that's changed.

96
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:29,375
