be cheating on me.

97
00:06:29,458 --> 00:06:31,041
[CHIAKI]
Are you serious?

98
00:06:31,125 --> 00:06:32,458
[KAHO]
Uh-huh.

99
00:06:32,541 --> 00:06:34,958
Looks like it's probably with
some girl named Sadako

100
00:06:35,041 --> 00:06:35,916
at his school.

101
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,041
He likes her.

102
00:06:37,125 --> 00:06:38,916
He wants to share
his snacks with her.

103
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:41,583
I mean, he even let her
have his favorite jump rope--

104
00:06:41,666 --> 00:06:44,416
the one his mom left him.

105
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:45,875
And that's not all!

106
00:06:45,958 --> 00:06:46,958
He thinks...

107
00:06:47,041 --> 00:06:48,625
...it feels so good
to hug Sadako

108
00:06:48,708 --> 00:06:50,833
that he never wants
to stop hugging her!

109
00:06:50,916 --> 00:06:53,458
