into participating.

191
00:09:56,041 --> 00:09:57,583
[KAHO]
Yeah, I can see that.

192
00:09:57,666 --> 00:09:59,166
Kaho, are you coming, too?

193
00:09:59,250 --> 00:10:01,500
Don't be silly.
Of course I am!

194
00:10:01,583 --> 00:10:02,625
[KANADE]
Awesome!

195
00:10:15,375 --> 00:10:16,708
[KAHO]
Will you please move?

196
00:10:16,791 --> 00:10:19,583
[TAGA]
Boy, you have got some nerve.

197
00:10:19,666 --> 00:10:22,416
Especially considering
you read that diary.

198
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:24,625
Yeah. Well, excuse me.

199
00:10:24,708 --> 00:10:26,000
[TAGA chuckles]

200
00:10:26,083 --> 00:10:28,875
Now... as for
tomorrow's festival...

201
00:10:28,958 --> 00:10:30,416
See you there, garbage girl.

202
00:10:39,583 --> 00:10:41,875
[ANNOUNCER 11A] It's time to
kick off Bamboo Primary School's

203
00:10:41,958 --> 00:10:43,416
annual sports festival!

204
00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:45,458
[CROWD clapping]

205
00:10:49,416 --> 00:10:52,125
[ARASHI] Yes! There are
so many cuties here!

206
00:10:52,208 --> 00:10:54,000
But where are
Kanade and his friends?

207
00:10:54,083 --> 00:10:55,875
Um... I think I found 'em.

208
00:10:59,041 --> 00:11:02,208
Well, no chance we'll
ever lose sight of that crew.

209
00:11:02,291 --> 00:11:05,125
[ANNOUNCER 11A]
Begin the warm-up exercises.

210
00:11:05,208 --> 00:11:09,083
And remember, children,
give yourselves plenty of room!

211
00:11:09,166 --> 00:11:15,208
One, two, three, four,
five, six, seven, eight...

212
00:11:17,333 --> 00:11:18,375
[yells]

213
