Oh, they stand out.

216
00:11:25,083 --> 00:11:27,041
But whether that's
for better or for worse...

217
00:11:27,125 --> 00:11:28,458
Yeah, no comment.

218
00:11:28,541 --> 00:11:32,041
Ah! I'm gonna take
some of the best shots today!

219
00:11:32,125 --> 00:11:34,375
[ANNOUNCER 11A] Next up
is the fifth-grade ball-toss.

220
00:11:34,458 --> 00:11:35,625
--[ARASHI] Ball-toss!
--[whistle blows]

221
