[CHIAKI]
Is that fair?

222
00:11:47,333 --> 00:11:49,125
It doesn't seem fair.

223
00:11:49,208 --> 00:11:50,916
[MAFUYU] Wow, they're
literally head and shoulders

224
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:52,458
above the rest, aren't they?

225
00:11:52,541 --> 00:11:53,583
[LEIA]
Hey, boys!

226
00:11:53,666 --> 00:11:54,958
Don't be selfish.

227
00:11:55,041 --> 00:11:57,041
You need to give all us
girls a chance to play, too!

228
