Red team, go!

244
00:12:31,541 --> 00:12:34,250
Red team, fight!

245
00:12:34,333 --> 00:12:37,291
Go get 'em, go! Go! Go!

246
00:12:37,375 --> 00:12:40,500
Yeah! Give 'em
that fightin' spirit!

247
00:12:40,583 --> 00:12:44,250
